Michael J. DOBRUCK, Petitioner, v. DEPARTMENT OF VETERANS AFFAIRS, Respondent. No. 2006-3411. United States Court of Appeals, Federal Circuit. March 15, 2007. Michael J. Dobruck, pro se.

Before MICHEL, Chief Judge, DYK, Circuit Judge, and PROST, Circuit Judge.

ORDER

A petition for rehearing having been filed by the Petitioner, and a response thereto having been invited by the court and filed by the Respondent,

UPON CONSIDERATION THEREOF, it is

ORDERED that the petition for rehearing be, and the same hereby is, DENIED.

The mandate of the court will issue on March 22, 2007.
